  "onboarding.ollamaTitle": "Local AI with Ollama",
  "onboarding.ollamaSubtitle": "Liminal can run entirely on your machine using Ollama.\nNo API keys, no cloud — your data stays local.\n\nThis is optional. You can also use Claude or OpenAI.",
  "onboarding.ollamaSteps": "How to set up:",
  "onboarding.ollamaStep1": "Download and install Ollama",
  "onboarding.ollamaStep2": "Open Ollama — it runs in the background",
  "onboarding.ollamaStep3": "Choose a model in Settings > LLM",
  "onboarding.ollamaChecking": "Checking for Ollama…",
  "onboarding.ollamaDetected": "Ollama is running",
  "onboarding.ollamaNotDetected": "Ollama not detected",
  "onboarding.ollamaRecheck": "Recheck",
  "onboarding.ollamaSettingsHint": "You can configure your LLM provider anytime in Settings.",
  "onboarding.done": "You’re all set.",
  "onboarding.doneSubtitle": "Your portrait has been saved.\nYour responses will use this context from your very first entry.\n\nYou can update your portrait anytime from the sidebar.",
  "onboarding.startJournaling": "Start journaling",
  "onboarding.disclaimerHeading": "Before we begin",
  "onboarding.disclaimerBody1": "Liminal is a journaling companion, not a therapist, doctor, or psychologist. The reflections you receive are AI-generated — sometimes surprisingly insightful, sometimes way off. Think of it as a thoughtful friend with a good bookshelf, not a licensed professional.",
  "onboarding.disclaimerBody2": "If you’re going through something heavy — grief, crisis, dark thoughts — please reach out to a real human. A counsellor, a helpline, someone who knows you. Liminal can’t replace that, and it isn’t trying to.",
  "onboarding.disclaimerCrisisLabel": "Crisis resources:",
  "onboarding.disclaimerCrisisSuffix": "(EU) — or visit befrienders.org",
  "onboarding.disclaimerClosing": "That said — if you show up honestly, you might be surprised what comes back. Trust the process, but tie your camel.",
  "onboarding.quiz.skipQuiz": "Skip quiz",
  "onboarding.quiz.adjustAnytime": "You can adjust this anytime.",
  "onboarding.quiz.q1.question": "What tools do you use to understand yourself?",
  "onboarding.quiz.q1.witness": "Therapy, journaling, reading — understanding through reflection",
  "onboarding.quiz.q1.seeker": "Meditation, breathwork, sacred practice — understanding through stillness",
  "onboarding.quiz.q1.attuned": "Tarot, nature cycles, ritual — understanding through symbol and pattern",
  "onboarding.quiz.q2.question": "When something difficult happens, your first instinct is to:",
  "onboarding.quiz.q2.witness": "Understand it — trace it back, find the pattern, make sense of it",
  "onboarding.quiz.q2.seeker": "Feel through it — sit with it, let something larger hold it",
  "onboarding.quiz.q2.attuned": "Trust the timing — something in you knows this has its own season",
  "onboarding.quiz.q3.question": "Which of these phrases feels most like you?",
  "onboarding.quiz.q3.witness": "I’m working through something",
  "onboarding.quiz.q3.seeker": "I’m being called toward something",
  "onboarding.quiz.q3.attuned": "Something is shifting",
  "onboarding.quiz.q4.question": "What’s most likely on your bookshelf?",
  "onboarding.quiz.q4.witness": "Psychology, behaviour, the examined life — making sense of why we are the way we are",
  "onboarding.quiz.q4.seeker": "Contemplative writing, philosophy, anything that points toward presence",
  "onboarding.quiz.q4.attuned": "Mythology, symbolism, the natural world, ancient wisdom traditions",
  "onboarding.quiz.q5.question": "Your ideal morning practice looks like:",
  "onboarding.quiz.q5.witness": "Journaling, reading, a walk — grounded and reflective",
  "onboarding.quiz.q5.seeker": "Meditation or breathwork — something intentional and still",
  "onboarding.quiz.q5.attuned": "Something intuitive — a card, a moment with the sky, setting an intention",
  "onboarding.quiz.q6.question": "When you think about personal growth, the language that resonates most is:",
  "onboarding.quiz.q6.witness": "Patterns, healing, understanding, integration",
  "onboarding.quiz.q6.seeker": "Awakening, surrender, presence, the sacred",
  "onboarding.quiz.q6.attuned": "Cycles, symbols, timing, the bigger picture",
  "onboarding.quiz.q7.question": "Your relationship with intuition is:",
  "onboarding.quiz.q7.witness": "Something I’m learning to trust alongside logic",
  "onboarding.quiz.q7.seeker": "A practice I actively cultivate and return to",
  "onboarding.quiz.q7.attuned": "Something I’ve always followed — it usually knows before I do",
  "onboarding.quiz.result.witness.label": "The Witness",
  "onboarding.quiz.result.seeker.label": "The Seeker",
  "onboarding.quiz.result.attuned.label": "The Attuned",
